data.description: Discover the perfect blend of modern luxury and timeless charm in this meticulously upgraded 992 square feet ranch in Lakewood, Ohio. Renovated in 2017, this home features all-new cabinets, granite countertops, and tile flooring, while ensuring safety with updated wiring from knob and tube. Revel in the warmth of a gas fireplace with a new flute in the chimney and embrace the convenience of a fully finished basement with new flooring, ceiling fixtures, and a closet added in 2019. Modern amenities include an air conditioning system, a water tank, and blown-in insulation, all installed in 2017. The exterior boasts brand new garage doors with openers, a side man door, and a new privacy fence in the backyard for outdoor seclusion. Additional updates include new cedar doors, bathroom vent, and a base heater in the basement. The house and garage roofs were both installed in 2017, ensuring durability and curb appeal. This home is a true haven, seamlessly blending comfort and functionality.
